This application could help users track their medications, set reminders for
dosage times, and update their medication routine as prescribed by a doctor.
It uses methods such as:

set_reminder(self, new_time_of_day) method:
Takes new_time_of_day as an argument from outside.

Updates self.time_of_day and marks self.reminder_set = True.
update_dosage(self, new_dosage) method:
Updates the dosage if needed.

info(self) method:
Displays all current information.